      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at Model Risk Level 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty assessment not required at MRL 2. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model is an accepted industry standard for this device class."
    },
    {
